#compdef maelstrom-broker
# Documentation: source-direct extraction from upstream
# maelstrom-software/maelstrom —
#   crates/maelstrom-broker/src/config.rs lines 60-119
#     (Config struct: 8 flags including 1 cfg-gated on
#     `web-ui` feature + 3 hidden flags)
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-30 via gh api.
#
# maelstrom-broker is the **Maelstrom broker daemon** — the
# central coordinator that workers connect to and that test-
# runner clients (R238 cargo-maelstrom, R239 maelstrom-
# pytest/go-test/run) submit jobs to.  Runs as a long-lived
# service; one broker per Maelstrom cluster.  Sister daemons
# in the corpus's R240 round: maelstrom-worker (the per-node
# job executor) and maelstrom-admin (the admin CLI from R240).
#
# Critical extraction note: maelstrom-broker has the SMALLEST
# CLI surface of the Maelstrom infrastructure trio — 8 flags
# total, with `--port` defaulting to 0 (let OS pick) and
# `--cache-size` defaulting to 1 GB.  Long-lived service
# expected to be configured via the maelstrom-broker.toml
# config file rather than CLI flags in production use.  The
# CLI flags are primarily for ad-hoc testing.
#
# Critical extraction note: `-H`/`--http-port` flag at
# config.rs:67-69 is **CFG-GATED on `feature = "web-ui"`** —
# only available when the broker is built with the web-ui
# feature.  Continues R233 regorus's feature-gating
# documentation (variant-level + body-bail + inner-flag
# patterns).  This is the corpus's first documented
# **feature-gated single flag** on a Config-derive struct.
# Completion lists it unconditionally since installed binary
# features are opaque.
#
# Critical extraction note: `--port`/`-p` defaulting to `0`
# is the Linux convention for "let the OS pick an unused
# port" — the broker logs the actual bound port at startup
# so workers can connect.  Documented in completion
# description.

_arguments -s -S \
  '(-h --help)'{-h,--help}'[show help and exit]' \
  '(-V --version)'{-V,--version}'[show version and exit]' \
  '(-p --port)'{-p+,--port=}'[port for workers + client connections (default 0 = OS-picked)]:port:' \
  '(-H --http-port)'{-H+,--http-port=}'[(feature: web-ui) HTTP UI port (default 0 = OS-picked)]:port:' \
  '--cache-root=[directory for the cache (default: $XDG_CACHE_HOME/maelstrom-broker)]:path:_files -/' \
  '--cache-size=[target disk space for cache (SI/binary suffixes; default 1GB)]:bytes:' \
  '(-L --log-level)'{-L+,--log-level=}'[min log level (default info)]:level:(error warn info debug trace)' \
  '--cluster-communication-strategy=[(HIDDEN) cluster strategy]:strategy:(tcp github)' \
  '--github-actions-token=[(HIDDEN) ACTIONS_RUNTIME_TOKEN]:token:' \
  '--github-actions-url=[(HIDDEN) ACTIONS_RESULTS_URL]:url:_urls'
